    }
  },
  "small_print": "FHA and VA loans will require that you deliver to the seller a list of any lender required repairs or conditions that you want the seller to pay for or otherwise correct or a statement that there are no lender requirements. Keep in mind that the seller has no obligation to pay or satisfy any or all lender requirements unless agreed to in writing.",
